::Reptilica::

Reptilica lands in the forest, walking forward. He looks around. He seemed to 
have lost DevilDuer somewhere. Reptilica shruggs. That bot was never any help 
anyways.

The Alliance bot looks down at his scanner. According to it, the new bot was 
.... right above him! Reptilica jumps back, looking up to see a large spotted 
cat creature.

"Hey there," he yells over to it, trying to sound friendly, "I'm Reptilica, 
what's your name?"
